## Error States

### Standard Error State

```typescript
const ErrorState: React.FC<{ error?: Error }> = ({ error }) => {
  return (
    <div className='aucctus-bg-primary flex min-h-[400px] items-center justify-center'>
      <div className='text-center'>
        <Icon
          variant='alert-circle'
          className='aucctus-stroke-error-primary mx-auto mb-4 h-12 w-12'
        />
        <div className='aucctus-text-xl aucctus-text-primary mb-2'>
          Error Loading Data
        </div>
        <div className='aucctus-text-md aucctus-text-secondary mb-4'>
          {error?.message || 'There was an error loading the data.'}
        </div>
        <button 
          className='btn btn-primary btn-md'
          onClick={() => window.location.reload()}
        >
          Try Again
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
```

### Inline Error State

For smaller components:

```typescript
const InlineErrorState: React.FC = () => (
  <div className='aucctus-bg-error-subtle aucctus-border-error rounded border p-4'>
    <div className='flex items-start gap-3'>
      <Icon 
        variant='alert-triangle' 
        className='aucctus-stroke-error-primary h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0' 
      />
      <div>
        <p className='aucctus-text-sm-semibold aucctus-text-error-primary mb-1'>
          Unable to load data
        </p>
        <p className='aucctus-text-xs aucctus-text-secondary'>
          Please try again or contact support if the problem persists.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
);
```

### Error State with Retry

```typescript
const ErrorStateWithRetry: React.FC<{ onRetry: () => void }> = ({ onRetry }) => (
  <div className='flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-8'>
    <Icon 
      variant='alert-octagon' 
      className='aucctus-stroke-error-primary h-12 w-12' 
    />
    <div className='text-center'>
      <h3 className='aucctus-text-md-semibold aucctus-text-primary mb-2'>
        Something went wrong
      </h3>
      <p className='aucctus-text-sm aucctus-text-secondary mb-4'>
        We couldn't load this content. Please try again.
      </p>
      <button className='btn btn-primary btn-md' onClick={onRetry}>
        Retry
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
);
```

